    </div>
    <div class="col s12 m8 offset-m3">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-content">
          <p>
            Michael Bertoldi’s main focus is delivering practical solutions to clients who need his assistance.  Michael believes that, in many situations, clients are better served by the certainty of settlement rather than the expense of litigation, which is a result of his focused and persistent attitude towards his clients and their files.  Michael provides each client with all of their legal options, and Michael then works with his clients to achieve the best result possible in the circumstances.
          </p><br>
          <div class="divider"></div>
          <p><br>
            Michael firmly believes that a small firm offers clients real advantages. First, a small firm is able to provide a personal level of service that many clients find pleasantly surprising.  Secondly, a small firm can provide competitive rates to its clients.  Thirdly, a small firm setting ensures continuity for each file, and allows the same lawyer to see a particular file through from beginning to end in most cases.  Michael Bertoldi believes that most clients find that they are better served in the smaller, more personal environment of a small firm.
          </p><br>
          <div class="divider"></div>
          <br>
          <p>
            If you have any litigation questions, please feel free to contact Michael at your convenience: mike@bert-law.com / FAX: 604.677.5640 / TEL: 604.628.9333
          </p>
        </div>
